data.description: RENTED TIL 12/31/2024! BUILT IN 2022 TOWNHOUSE WITH 1-CAR GARAGE IN RIVIERA COMMUNITY! Features a smart home system, tile flooring throughout 1st floor, and carpet flooring on the 2nd floor. Kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops overlooking the family area. Master bedroom with master bathroom en-suite features dual sinks and spacious walk-in shower. Hurrican shutter. Community amenities offer a pool, Gym, and clubhouse. Maintenance includes front yard landscaping. Located near the Turnpike.
